    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1888-01-18">Jan: 18 '88<ptr target="nyp.00693_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute/>
            </opener>

            <p>Nothing very new with me. Storms, snow &#38; cold weather. I send the <hi rend="italic">Harvard Monthly</hi><ptr target="nyp.00693_n2"/>&#8212;
                when thro' send to Dr Bucke.<ptr target="n0119"/> I am pottering along&#8212;certainly no worse in my late physical
                ailments&#8212;rather better possibly&#8212;the wind is sighing &#38; singing &#38; piping around the house as I write.</p>
            
            <closer>
                <salute/>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
